Lucky Dice – Privacy Policy

Last Updated: March 24, 2026

Lucky Dice (“we”, “our”, “us”) respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect information from players of our game.

1. Information We Collect

We may collect the following information:

Device & Technical Information
Device type, operating system, and version
Game progress, achievements, and in-game currency
Analytics data for improving gameplay
Advertising & Analytics
If you interact with ads, we may use third-party advertising services (like AdMob) that collect device identifiers and activity data to serve relevant ads
This data is anonymized and aggregated
Personal Information
We do not knowingly collect personally identifiable information (such as name, email, or phone number) from any player
We do not target or track users under 13 years old
2. How We Use Information

We use collected information to:

Improve game performance and user experience
Analyze gameplay trends for updates and bug fixes
Provide customer support
Display non-personalized or interest-based advertisements
3. Data Sharing
We do not sell or share personal information with third parties
We may share aggregated and anonymized data with partners for analytics purposes
Third-party ad networks may collect information as described above
4. Children’s Privacy
Our game is intended for all ages
We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13
Parents or guardians can contact us to delete any data collected from their children
5. Security

We implement reasonable security measures to protect the information we collect. However, no system can be 100% secure.

